about.about_text: I am passionate about programming. Since 2017 I have been dedicating myself to learning and developing new programming skills. I love trying new things and I'm always looking to learn about new technologies. I currently share my projects through my GitHub. I find it amazing how programming allows me to create new things and solve complex problems. I am a dedicated and determined person. I want to continue learning and evolving as a programmer, and I am sure that one day I will achieve my goals.
